text: Henri Cuq (12 March 1942 - 11 June 2010) was a member of the National Assembly of France. He represented the Yvelines department, and was a member of the Union for a Popular Movement. ==References== Category:1942 births Category:2010 deaths Category:People from Toulouse Category:Politicians from Occitanie Category:Rally for the Republic politicians Category:Union for a Popular Movement politicians Category:Government ministers of France Category:Deputies of the 12th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic Category:Deputies of the 13th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic Category:Deaths from cancer in France
title: Henri Cuq
